{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>BetterYou 是一款專為提升個人專注力與工作效率而設計的 App，今天限時免費中。它能有效幫助您擺脫智能裝置的誘惑，無論是學生需要高效學習、專業人士追求深度工作，還是想擁有良好睡眠品質的使用者，都能透過這款應用輕鬆打造專屬的專注環境，讓數位生活更有規劃。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-93.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>高度客製化專注模式</h2>\n    <p>這款應用提供了高度客製化的專注模式，您可以根據不同情境設定專屬限制，並透過內建預設或自訂圖示與色彩。它具備兩階段承諾模式，普通模式允許短暫休息並設有冷卻期，而硬核模式則完全移除中斷與提前退出選項，確保您達到最大程度的鎖定專注。此外，應用還支援實時活動，讓您能在鎖定畫面與動態島上查看專注時長，並提供詳細的進度圖表，讓您的努力成果一目瞭然。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-158-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-159-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-160-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-161-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-162-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-163-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：BetterYou: Screen Time Control</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Productivity</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-25T14:58:03.649834+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":379,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}